{
    "data": [
        {
            "title": "CFA三級考試通過率升至50% 仍低於十年平均水平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"852\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wtFasCHS1bc68MqQM.7rug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg1MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/55f11909a257cc611f43b63db94d5065\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 特許金融分析師(CFA)最終級別考試的通過率小幅上升，但仍低於歷史平均水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CFA協會周四表示，今年8月有50%考生通過三級考試，比例高於2月的49%以及去年同期的48%。儘管如此，該成績仍低於過去10年51%的平均通過率。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">8月三級考試首次允許考生根據個人興趣選擇三種「專業路徑」之一，包括私人財富管理、私募市場，或傳統的投資組合管理。CFA協會表示，三種路徑「同樣嚴格」，無論選擇哪一條，成功通過考試後將獲得CFA認證。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-46b5d4a1-1611-359f-a5fb-d87ce3a7dcbf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S08HK_K7vHgjnYfUUzyWDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg1MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7fff97ba151b69ea51a0c0ef0536acab\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">協會同時指出，推遲考試的考生通過率明顯較低。CFA協會教育事務董事總經理Chris Wiese表示，首次參加考試的考生表現顯著高於平均水平，通過率為59%；而至少推遲過一次考試的考生通過率僅為33%。他建議考生應儘量按計畫參加考試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">8月參加一級和二級考試的考生已於本月初收到成績。一級通過率為43%，二級為44%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題CFA Final Success Rate Climbs to 50% While Below Decade Average</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/cfa%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E8%80%83%E8%A9%A6%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%8E%87%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B350-%E4%BB%8D%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-142835425.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-23 23:20:53",
