        {
            "title": "波音中國換帥 新負責人有駐華經歷並通曉中文",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cTqajw2HaXlm5LIrkCpjLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b0114dd51f1647c6a959aa5c5c660baa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 波音任命Landon Loomis負責在華業務，這家美國飛機製造商在應對日益加劇的地緣政治緊張局勢的同時，試圖爭取來自中國的訂單。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司聲明稱，Loomis即日起上任。他之前負責波音在巴西的業務，在加入波音前曾擔任時任美國副總統邁克·彭斯的特別顧問。彭博新聞社周四早些時候率先報導了這一任命。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據內部通知，Loomis曾在美國駐華大使館工作逾五年，負責航空事務，並能說普通話。他接替Carol Shen出任該職位，後者在今年早些時候柳青離職後獲任為臨時總裁。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dde92e70-713c-3451-92f4-65eb04bcd8ef-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">波音總裁Brendan Nelson表示，Loomis的首要任務是利用他在中國積累的行業和政府經驗，繼續拓展波音在中國的業務。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Landon Loomis攝影師：Tarina Rodriguez/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PpuX6WnPPESNTd.zhD8plw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8bb77bc59acac4c74172db8998e764e5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Landon Loomis攝影師：Tarina Rodriguez/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀： 波音對華談判據悉邁向衝刺 多達500架飛機的大單取決於中美關係走向</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Boeing Names Landon Loomis as China Head Before Trade Talks (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julie Johnsson、李嘉洪.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%9B%E5%B8%A5-%E6%96%B0%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E4%B8%A6%E9%80%9A%E6%9B%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87-114333542.html",
