        {
            "title": "中國「十五五」規劃要求科技自立自強水平大幅提高 建設強大國內市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國誓言在未來五年加快高水平科技自立自強並建設強大國內市場，旨在讓經濟免受外部壓力影響的同時，打造可持續的成長引擎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為期四天的中共第二十屆中央委員會第四次全體會議會議結束後，央視周四發布會議公報稱，全會提出「十五五」時期經濟社會發展的主要目標，科技自立自強水平要「大幅提高」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全會提出要引領發展「新質生產力」，指的是半導體和人工智能等先進技術。這反映出面對人口老齡化及西方對高科技出口的限制，北京正致力於提升生產力並實現自給自足。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c171df52-f42d-3b2a-83e1-f308a4b85927-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，公報重申要大力提振消費。經濟學家長期以來一直認為，這對於實現經濟再平衡、減少對出口和債務驅動型投資的依賴至關重要，不過任何新的政策措施預計將於稍後公佈。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Deepens Bid for Tech Self-Reliance in New Development Plan</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%94%E4%BA%94-%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%87%AA%E7%AB%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%BC%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98-%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-092611593.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-23 18:05:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國制裁俄羅斯石油巨頭 引發中國業界擔憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國制裁俄羅斯石油巨頭 引發中國業界擔憂\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kbJB6rQ5d5N1NgJ0539rOg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/b9f24c20-b003-11f0-a7bf-f255b6fedb3b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國制裁俄羅斯石油巨頭 引發中國業界擔憂</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD-%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-100213105.html",
