            "title": "拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮　入職10年獲贈100克金磚",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮，入職10年獲贈100克黃金。(網上圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/17m.XKXZIqO7._AOdAdkIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/c6de9506d7fa9db5d7b0a84f6de3cdc9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮，入職10年獲贈100克黃金。(網上圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>據內媒報道，內地電商平台拼多多(美：PDD)迎來10周年之際，為感謝員工長期貢獻，公司推出「十周年禮」，根據員工的工作年期，贈送不同規格的禮品。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">按年資分級贈禮 金戒指到金磚顯誠意</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span>不少拼多多員工都在</span></span></span>社交平台上分享了他們收到的黃金禮品照片。據報道<span><span><span><span><span>，入職滿3年的員工，獲贈一枚刻有本人姓名的金戒指，重量約4克；入職滿5年的員工，金戒指重量提升至11克；而對入職已滿10年的資深員工，拼多多則贈送一塊重達100克的</span></span></span></span>金雞<span><span><span><span>，以表彰他們的忠誠付出。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">今年<span><span><span><span><span>金雞大增40克</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>報道提到，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>與去年相比，拼多多今年贈送的</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>金禮克數普遍增加。去年，入職3年、5年和10年員工對應的贈禮分別為約4克金戒指、10.99克金戒指和60克金雞，而今年10年員工的贈禮克數更是大幅提升40克。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮-入職10年獲贈100克金磚/611313?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮-入職10年獲贈100克金磚/611313?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/拼多多十周年向員工送厚禮-入職10年獲贈100克金磚/611313?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
